Welcome to Muzain. Muzain is a cutting-edge mobile app designed to streamline booking services from salons or freelancers. We are dedicated to protecting your privacy and ensuring that your personal information is handled with the utmost care. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our app.

2. Information We Collect

We collect several types of information to provide and improve our services:

Personal Information: When you register an account or make a booking, we collect personal details such as your name, email address, phone number, and payment information.

Booking Details: Information related to the services you book, including appointment dates, times, and service provider details.

Usage Data: Data about how you interact with the app, including your IP address, device type, operating system, and browsing activities.

Communication Records: Information from your interactions with our customer support or any feedback you provide.

3. How We Use Your Information

We use your information for various purposes, including:

Service Delivery: To process and manage your bookings, appointments, and payments.

App Improvement: To analyze app usage and enhance functionality and user experience.

Communication: To send you updates, notifications, and promotional offers. You can opt out of marketing communications at any time.

Security: To protect against fraud and ensure the safety and integrity of our app and its users.

4. Sharing Your Information

We may share your information in the following situations:

With Service Providers: To facilitate bookings and transactions with salons or freelancers.

With Your Consent: When you authorize us to share your information with third parties for specific purposes.

For Legal Requirements: To comply with legal obligations, enforce our policies, or protect our rights and the safety of our users.

5. Data Security

We implement robust security measures to safeguard your information from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. However, while we strive to protect your data, no system is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute protection.

6. Your Rights and Choices

Access and Update: You can access and update your personal information by logging into your account.

Opt-Out: You may opt-out of receiving promotional communications by following the unsubscribe instructions provided in those messages.

Deletion Requests: You can request the deletion of your personal information, subject to applicable legal and contractual obligations.

7. Third-Party Links

Our app may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for their privacy practices. We encourage you to review their privacy policies before sharing any personal information.

8. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Significant changes will be communicated through our app or other appropriate methods. Your continued use of Muzain after such changes signifies your acceptance of the updated Privacy Policy.

